version_description:
We've squashed some bugs in this release, including:
-Fixed a bug that displayed a blank page after closing an End Card;
-Fixed missing loading spinner after End Card display;
-Made some analytics tweaks.

We're constantly working to deliver the best app experience to you.
Fixed in this version:
-Blank screen was displaying when user logged in via Live player;
-Implemented Loading Indicators Before Playing Video;
-Blank Schedule was displaying when user closed the Live player.
